  "translations": [
    {
      "language": "uk",
      "displayName": "Навігатор Markdown",
      "description": "Додаток NVDA, що забезпечує структуровану навігацію (заголовки, списки, таблиці тощо) у редагованих текстових областях для файлів Markdown.",
      "changelog": "### 0.2.7\n\n- Simplified Markdown navigation internals to reduce duplicated code.\n- Improved caret positioning consistency in Chrome and Edge web editors.\n- Removed the old legacy navigation fallback now that the fast navigation path is the main implementation.\n\nNote: If a text editor does not support the fast navigation path, Markdown navigation may no longer fall back to the older slower method."
    },
    {
      "language": "ru",
      "displayName": "Markdown-навигатор",
      "description": "Дополнение для NVDA, обеспечивающее структурную навигацию (заголовки, списки, таблицы и т.д.) в редактируемых текстовых областях для Markdown-файлов.",
      "changelog": "### 0.2.7\n\n- Simplified Markdown navigation internals to reduce duplicated code.\n- Improved caret positioning consistency in Chrome and Edge web editors.\n- Removed the old legacy navigation fallback now that the fast navigation path is the main implementation.\n\nNote: If a text editor does not support the fast navigation path, Markdown navigation may no longer fall back to the older slower method."
    },
    {
      "language": "zh_CN",
      "displayName": "Markdown 导航",
      "description": "一个 NVDA 插件，为 Markdown 文件提供结构化导航（标题、列表、表格等）。",
      "changelog": "### 0.2.7\n\n- Simplified Markdown navigation internals to reduce duplicated code.\n- Improved caret positioning consistency in Chrome and Edge web editors.\n- Removed the old legacy navigation fallback now that the fast navigation path is the main implementation.\n\nNote: If a text editor does not support the fast navigation path, Markdown navigation may no longer fall back to the older slower method."
    }
  ],
